OL,3,CGirl makes 'amazing' recovery after
OL,4,Cbeing 'broken in half' from horse fall
OL,6,FA teenage girl who was "broken in
OL,7,Fhalf" after falling from her horse and
OL,8,Ftold that she might never walk again
OL,9,Fhas made an "amazing" recovery by
OL,10,Fwalking out of hospital unaided.
OL,12,FAliza Rae AliKhan was rushed into
OL,13,Femergency spinal surgery after her
OL,14,Fhorse was spooked and fell on top of
OL,15,Fher in the accident in August last
OL,16,Fyear.
