OL,6,F"We just needed to stay positive for
OL,7,Fthe sake of Aliza Rae. She was
OL,8,Fconscious and she was talking, so we
OL,9,Fjust focused on that and went from
OL,10,Fthere.
OL,12,F"We didn't know what the future would
OL,13,Fhold, but we knew we were in the best
OL,14,Fhands and Aliza Rae just kept focusing
OL,15,Fon what she could do, not what she
OL,16,Fcouldn't."
OL,18,FA further operation was carried out to
OL,19,Fremove small pieces of bone which were
OL,20,Fspotted in a follow-up X-ray.
