OL,3,CGirl makes 'amazing' recovery after
OL,4,Cbeing 'broken in half' from horse fall
OL,6,FAliza Rae was transferred to the
OL,7,Fpaediatric intensive care unit (PICU)
OL,8,Fwhere her bespoke rehabilitation
OL,9,Fregime began within 48 hours of her
OL,10,Fsurgery, led by the Southampton
OL,11,FChildren's Integrated Rehabilitation
OL,12,FTeam (SCIRT).
OL,14,FShe left the hospital just after her
OL,15,F13th birthday and returned to Hanford
OL,16,FPrep school where she is preparing for
OL,17,Fupcoming exams and planning a
OL,18,Ffundraising event for the hospital.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
