OL,3,CGirl makes 'amazing' recovery after
OL,4,Cbeing 'broken in half' from horse fall
OL,6,FShe said: "I want to give something
OL,7,Fback to everyone that looked after me.
OL,8,FI remember being told I might never
OL,9,Fwalk again, but I had this amazing
OL,10,Fteam, my dream team, and they never
OL,11,Fgave up on me.
OL,13,F"They became like friends, not just
OL,14,Fdoctors and physios. They helped me
OL,15,Fbelieve in myself."
