OL,3,CGirl makes 'amazing' recovery after
OL,4,Cbeing 'broken in half' from horse fall
OL,6,FHer mother added: "The team were
OL,7,Famazing from day one. Positive,
OL,8,Fsupportive and really connected with
OL,9,FAliza Rae ` they had the right balance
OL,10,Fof pushing her and knowing when it was
OL,11,Ftoo much.
OL,13,F"We'll forever be grateful for
OL,14,Feverything that everyone at SCH has
OL,15,Fdone for Aliza Rae."
